00:19:12.678 --> 00:19:14.348
"Love is a battlefield."

491
00:19:14.437 --> 00:19:18.011
Pat was right. which I always
knew in my heart of hearts.

492
00:19:18.044 --> 00:19:21.350
- But. Brian. in my heart of hearts...
- [CHRIS] Too many.

493
00:19:21.417 --> 00:19:24.524
... I can't think of anyone
else I'd rather grow old with.

494
00:19:24.557 --> 00:19:26.061
But like a good kind of old.

495
00:19:26.094 --> 00:19:28.765
not ragged-looking because
we didn't wear sunscreen.

496
00:19:28.798 --> 00:19:30.636
Real talk. you got to
be better about that.

497
00:19:30.669 --> 00:19:32.173
But yes. Brian. yes.

498
00:19:32.173 --> 00:19:36.380
I will marry you and make
you the happiest dog on Earth.

499
00:19:38.252 --> 00:19:40.256
♪

500
00:19:41.292 --> 00:19:44.297
Since when can a dog and a
baby not get a marriage license?

501
00:19:44.308 --> 00:19:45.743
I can't even get an abortion.

502
00:19:45.832 --> 00:19:47.402
- Move.
- Whoa!

503
00:19:48.291 --> 00:19:50.395
Problem solved. Thank you.

504
00:19:50.542 --> 00:19:52.546
- Are we done here?
- Yes.

505
00:19:52.546 --> 00:19:54.216
[GASPS] We forgot about Chris.

506
00:19:54.305 --> 00:19:56.643
<i>[CHRIS] I wound up
marrying The Librarian</i>

507
00:19:56.654 --> 00:19:58.391
<i>so we wouldn't lose our deposit.</i>

508
00:19:58.458 --> 00:20:01.431
<i>She didn't know my age
and wound up going to jail.</i>

509
00:20:01.431 --> 00:20:03.368
<i>I told everyone we did it.</i>

510
00:20:03.379 --> 00:20:05.817
<i>They ended up making
a whole movie about it.</i>

511
00:20:05.906 --> 00:20:07.843
<i>They portrayed her as the aggressor.</i>

512
00:20:07.910 --> 00:20:10.315
<i>Anyway. my name is Chris Griffin.</i>

513
00:20:10.382 --> 00:20:11.684
<i>and I'm supposed to get</i>

514
00:20:11.684 --> 00:20:15.058
<i>a Quahog NAACP Image Award next week.</i>

515
00:20:19.567 --> 00:20:21.537
♪

516
00:20:22.213 --> 00:20:23.728
I know everybody's happy for us.

517
00:20:23.739 --> 00:20:26.982
but I wish Pornhub wouldn't
use the title "Beauty and Obese".

518
00:20:27.016 --> 00:20:29.253
You know what. Peter? I don't care.

519
00:20:29.253 --> 00:20:32.126
Maybe we're not as young
or hot as we used to be.

520
00:20:32.126 --> 00:20:34.731
but there's no one I'd
rather spend my life

521
00:20:34.731 --> 00:20:37.570
sweating dark yellow stains
into the mattress with.

522
00:20:37.603 --> 00:20:39.573
- You really mean that?
- Yes.

523
00:20:39.573 --> 00:20:41.110
I love you. Peter.

524
00:20:41.110 --> 00:20:44.818
Hang on. let me go get my
men's quadruple XL sex shirt.

525
00:20:44.851 --> 00:20:46.821
There's a bulldog with sunglasses on it.

526
00:20:46.855 --> 00:20:48.725
so you know it's for big dogs.

527
00:20:48.725 --> 00:20:50.629
Just shut up and kiss me.

528
00:20:50.696 --> 00:20:52.733
[MOANING SOFTLY]

529
00:20:52.767 --> 00:20:54.737
Peter...

530
00:20:54.737 --> 00:20:57.743
- [PLANE PASSING]
- Hold for plane. Hold for plane.

531
00:20:57.776 --> 00:21:00.674
All right. Gatorades
down. back on all fours.

